+/// Vanilla `WardenAnimation.WARDEN_EMERGE`: the 6.68s spawn rise out of the ground (NOT looping),
+/// `emergeAnimation.apply(emergeAnimationState, ageInTicks)`. Started when the synced `DATA_POSE`
+/// changes to `Pose.EMERGING`. The deep `posVec(0, -63, 0)` opening keyframe on the body and legs
+/// sinks the warden underground, then hauls it up. The renderer applies it only while the projected
+/// `warden_emerge_seconds >= 0`, clamping past the length to the resting final frame.
